text: What Will People Say? is a 1916 American silent drama movie directed by Alice Guy-Blaché and was based on the novel by Rupert Hughes. It stars Olga Petrova, Fritz De Lint, Fraunie Fraunholz, Zadee Burbank. ==Other websites== * Category:1916 drama movies Category:American silent movies Category:American drama movies Category:Movies based on books Category:Movies directed by Alice Guy-Blaché
